%% Diagram: Resumable upload state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Selected
    Selected --> Validated: magic-byte + size ok
    Validated --> Created: POST -> 201 Location
    Created --> Uploading: PATCH first chunk
    Uploading --> Uploading: PATCH ok / 204\n+ Upload-Offset
    Uploading --> Resyncing: network err / 409
    Resyncing --> Uploading: HEAD -> server offset\nbackoff + jitter
    Uploading --> ChecksumRetry: 460 mismatch
    ChecksumRetry --> Uploading: re-send same chunk
    Uploading --> Paused: user / page hidden
    Paused --> Resyncing: resume on visibility
    Uploading --> Expired: Upload-Expires elapsed
    Uploading --> Completed: offset == length
    Expired --> [*]
    Completed --> Finalizing: server commit
    Finalizing --> [*]
